          <title>Mike McCarthy won't return as the Cowboys' coach. Deion Sanders could be a candidate to replace him</title>
          <description><![CDATA[DALLAS (AP) — Mike McCarthy will not return as coach of the Dallas Cowboys, who are going on three decades since their last Super Bowl title, owner Jerry Jones said Monday. Jones said the organization and McCarthy mutually agreed to part ways.]]></description>
